name: Warung Balun
address: HCMJ+WX8, Menanga, Rendang, Karangasem Regency, Bali 80863, Indonesia
review 1: This restaurant doesn’t exist where it’s depicted on the map, if at all.  We drove a narrow worn road and found the spot but it’s just a house with a lady who thought we were mad to think a restaurant was here.
